[A503] Monument Way (Westbound) at the junction of [A1055] The Hale - Lane restrictions westbound to facilitate electrical cable placement works.

[A201] New Kent Road (Both directions) between Elephant Road and Balfour Street - Various restrictions to facilitate TfL improvement works. Between 06 January - 22 January, lane closures in both directions. Full westbound closure in place on the nights of 03, 04 March. Full eastbound closure in place on the nights of 04, 05 March.
[A205] Westhorne Avenue (Both directions) between Baring Road and (A20) Sidcup Road - Lane restrictions are in place to facilitate Thames Water works.
[A24] Upper Tooting Road (Both directions) at the junction of Beechcroft Road - Single alternate lane operated by temporary signals for utility works.
[A316] Chertsey Road (Both directions) at the junction of [A310] London Road - There are lane restrictions in place due to junction improvement works.

comments: [A200] Tooley Street (Both directions) at the junction of Boss Street - Lane restrictions in place to facilitate Southern Gas connection works.

[A3203] Lambeth Bridge (Both directions) between [A3212] Millbank and [A3036] A 3036 - Various restrictions during junction improvement works at either side of Lambeth Bridge. Currently restrictions are in place on all approaches and inner ring of Lambeth Roundabout. From 30 January 21:30 until 07 February 05:00, there will be nightly road closures of Lambeth Bridge, Lambeth Palace Road, Lambeth Road & Albert Embankment, with diversions in place via Westminster and Vauxhall Bridges.
[A404] High Road (Both directions) at the junction of [B4565] Wembley Hill Road - Temporary traffic signals in place to facilitate roadworks.
[A4127] Greenford Road (Both directions) at the junction of Rockware Avenue - Temporary traffic signals in place to facilitate roadworks
[A215] Walworth Road (Southbound) at the junction of [A3] Newington Butts - Lane restriction contained to southbound Walworth Road to facilitate scaffolding works.
[A1000] Great North Road (Both directions) at the junction of Lyonsdown Road - There are temporary traffic lights at this location while a utilities company carries out works.
[A4205] Praed Street (Both directions) at the junction of Sale Place - Road works are being carried out at this location under temporary signals.
